{{!
  PROFILE CUSTOM TABS SNIPPET

  This adds the "Inklings" tab to the character profile page tab list.

  FILE: ares-webportal/app/templates/components/profile-custom-tabs.hbs
  LOCATION: Inside the <ul> element

  STEP 1: Locate the file
  1. Open your game's ares-webportal/app/templates/components/profile-custom-tabs.hbs
  2. Find the <ul> element that contains the profile tab links (usually near the top)

  STEP 2: Find the insertion point
  3. Find the end of the <ul> (look for </ul>)
  4. Look for any existing <li> elements - you'll paste AFTER the last one

  STEP 3: Copy and paste
  5. Copy the <li> block below (between the markers)
  6. Paste it inside the <ul>, right before the </ul> closing tag
  7. Save the file

  IMPORTANT: DO NOT change the href="#inklings-tab-pane"
  It must match the id="inklings-tab-pane" in profile-custom.snippet.hbs
}}

  {{! ---START COPY HERE--- }}
  <li class="nav-item">
    <a class="nav-link" data-toggle="tab" href="#inklings-tab-pane">Inklings</a>
  </li>
  {{! ---END COPY--- }}
